verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Gaadah nidra potulanu lepedamu daahamugala
Vaaralaku saakshyamithumu vegamuga desha drimmarini
Paara droluchu thyaagu desu kristuni siluvache{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Ahankaarula nellara cherchedamu mahaa mutyamulanu
Vedajalledamu maa dukhamulella sahinchedamu
Nechcheludu Yesu kristuni siluvache{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Okkadeyagu thandri biddalaaraa chakkagaa nokkatiga
Nundu vaaralaaraa eppudunu manchi manassutho
Naduvudi mana raajagu Yesuni siluvache{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Vachchu baadhalananni sahinchedamu goppa paathaka
Kriyala roopaarchedamu rikhtudaina mana naadhuni
Chaatudamu shakhti raajuni shaanti siluvache{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Prajala nellara shishyula gaavintumu tejomayudaina
Thandrini prakatintumu ellavaariki swaagatha
Monarintumu bhodhakudu Yesu kristuni siluvache{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Adi yapostalula sabhanu yerparachi dittamuga thappu
Bodhala vidichedamu eppudunu oppugane
Nadichedamu goppa thandri Yesu kristu siluvache{/lang-eng}
